Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:26.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:45.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:54.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:00:59.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:03.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:27.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:32.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:39.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:51.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:05.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:54.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Fake passports?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:57.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,One for each of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:04.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine with me, but doesn't your country provide them for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the mainland, aren't you? {}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:12.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it something you can't tell your lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to ask a bunch of rude questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:20.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you getting angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:25.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:33.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I, Qin, will do my best for the love between you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:38.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's pointless! No matter what I- Pointless!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:45.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're onto us. Running away is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It would be best to ambush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me? I'll say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:05.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just giving a suggestion since your plan has a high chance of failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:10.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Nothing will come out of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In deference to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:12.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:15.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you saying we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Spread a rumor that you're going to sell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:24.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:27.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Our enemies will jump at the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what you're suggesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:40.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're wary of those who attacked me in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We can't run away from them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There is a doll watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is it nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Because I haven't called out to it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:03.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Spread a rumor that a doll will be on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:11.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A doll? This girl isn't a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:15.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Dolls are supposed to have stone cold expressions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:26.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see this kind of quality often!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely different from a normal doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:33.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Its observation spirit takes on a human form, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How much do they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:44.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Everything. He's even telling them that it has an observation specter with a human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:49.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it would be hard to reel in buyers in this area with a normal doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Should we just take this chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We will see how things play out for a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:00.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I don't think you should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:10.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I have no attachment to this body, \Nbut I think I'll consider your suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you keep quiet about the enemy's doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Were you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:01.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you were worried this whole time, why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where to go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you saying that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember what you just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.05,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me anything next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.11,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever is on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:01.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you forever, just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I got caught by a dangerous gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:25.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I knew bad people would get involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:29.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but these guys are too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:38.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We should run while we can! \NThere's no turning back if we go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They're not normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:51.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they even bothering? \NThey don't usually deal in dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:53.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why today of all days?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm interested in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:58.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:04.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard she had a human-shaped observation specter, \Nso I was wondering what kind of girl she'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:07.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like your average doll though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I didn't think we'd be meeting here, my lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were supposed to meet at Lo's store?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,How about this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Three thousand Hong Kong dollars? So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty million.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and look for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:46.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't let them lay a hand on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have gotten involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:02.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:10.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if she's the real thing or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What if I said no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:20.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't told to say that, then that means you're not a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:24.70,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what terrible things dolls are forced to suffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:29.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,they would never speak out of line in deference to their owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:35.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that you're basing your assumptions on a typical doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:39.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell what I am anymore when I am with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:46.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I am a doll or not, I had no intention of dealing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You were planning to kill us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:56.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to keep her quiet, so I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:20.76,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And how will you dodge them this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:45.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be a joke! What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:57.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not that way! Go right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:44.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. I just felt there was something different about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He's manipulating me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Her specter is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hide her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything hasty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:37.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If she is the real thing, then your strength has proven it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.14,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Black Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:49.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I received some information from a special guest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:57.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,that there was a woman with a human-shaped specter and her protector, a male contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:05.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The contractor is supposed to have great physical abilities and can manipulate electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:10.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You have the ability to stand on even terms with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:17.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,and that is exactly what proves you're the Black Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:24.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I had known it would turn out like this, I would have prepared better for my remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:31.60,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I strengthen my ability just a bit more, you will be completely crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:36.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I will give you some time. Think through it logically.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can no longer win against-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:03.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:08.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a doll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:12.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:21.01,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:47.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:50.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You should tell her yourself, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:57.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,She's no longer human, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:00.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her to come quickly to my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:02.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So you got her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,His bleeding has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Watch him for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not like I can stay in Hong Kong anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:44.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this money to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You even killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The wicked shall perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:02.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That doll seems to be the real Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:10.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it would be such a waste to kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:15.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So we will be parting ways, Madame Oreille.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
