Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:59.56,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the anti-contractor weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:05.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,With this, they won't have the upper hand anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:07.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you were able to miniaturize the Saturn Ring in only 18 months!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:17.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Should we also take into consideration the effects it will have on humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:21.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We're blasting them with anti-Gate particles! \NThere's no way it would affect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:24.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But contractors will just die and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:28.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if we do the opposite and hit them with Gate particles?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:29.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:32.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They become more powerful contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:36.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.73,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Sawasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.27,0:22:47.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:51.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, chief! We may be able to put that item to good use in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:57.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then leave the rest to the researchers and fly to Hong Kong immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:02.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The ones we hired to capture the doll have been found dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:05.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami has awakened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:07.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any of the details yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:14.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,However, ever since BK-201 left Tokyo, the seriousness of the situation has been accelerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:17.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I sent someone to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:20.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ask them for the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:23.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:37.31,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sawasaki. It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:52.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Um... your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:24:04.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Picked up by the remnants of the EPR, we find a moment of repose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:07.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,However, that would not continue for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:13.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The jungle rain bores into us like rust bores into rock.